'''Turukiya''' (izina mu [[giturukiya]] : ''Türkiye'' ) ni [[igihugu]] mu [[Burayi]] na [[Aziya]]. [[Umurwa]] mukuru wa Turukiya witwa [[Ankara]]. Igihugu kiratuwe n’abaturage bagera kuri 78,785,548<ref>[https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/tu.html CIA]</ref>, batuye ku buso bwa km² 814.578.

[[Indirimbo y’Igihugu]] ni : [[İstiklâl Marşı]].
[[File:View_from_Mardin_to_the_Mesopotamian_plains.jpg|thumb|View from Mardin to the Mesopotamian plains]]

